    <item>
      <title>当关税焦虑重建以来，美元自10月以来最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/swiss-franc-surges-most-since-2015-yen-gains-on-rush-to-havens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国和中国之间的贸易紧张局势加剧了市场的延长，彭博社的彭博格量表降至最低，从而促进了市场的波动，并使全球增长的前景变黑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/swiss-franc-surges-most-since-2015-yen-gains-on-rush-to-havens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 16:08:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票中残酷的逆转显示特朗普关税波动的危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/traders-caught-offside-lament-swings-fomented-by-trump-flip-flop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街的另一种暴力逆转，这是一场股票的突发事件，在某一时刻消除了周三历史性收益的一半，这使投资者遇到了困难，试图驾驶现代历史上最不连贯的贸易政策之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/traders-caught-offside-lament-swings-fomented-by-trump-flip-flop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 15:50:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国30年债券拍卖会减轻对买家罢工的最坏的恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在满足30年期债券的拍卖需求强劲后，29万亿美元国库市场的投资者获得了稳定的稳定剂量。]]></description>
